Please find enclosed UPBGE 0.3 Pinball V2.8 Game Upgrade (Recommended Graphic Card Nvidia Gforce 2070 & an intel i7).

1 - 4 Player selection,1 -3 Ball selection, High score Board, Targets & loop rankers, Loop circuit, Ball saver, Auto plunger, Bonus scores,
Dmd animations, Table Animations, Ball color change, MultiBall, Ball Trailer, Plunger Lane & Spinner hinge actuators.

1. Bug fixes.
2. Ball trailer with image runner added
3. In ‘Render Properties’ do not check the ‘Use Viewport Render box’
4. In ‘Game Play Camera Mode’ under ‘Viewport Shading’ check that the ‘Scene Lights’ check box has been checked.
5. In Edit / Preferences / Addons check Game Engine Logic Nodes. Else ball trailer will not run.

Please enjoy & rob what you can from it if you wish.

Upgrades with bug fixes to Pinball V2.8 can be downloaded from:

https://www.dropbox.com/s/tsmezozr1jcm0yf/UPGBE%20Pinball%20V2.2.Blend?dl=0

Load the game using UPBGE(0.3). The Game mode will show first (Out off Edit Mode Press 'P' or standalone start to get it up & running) 

Keyboard instruction will appear & the rest is all down to the user.

VP forum holds four more tables that I have worked on: PacMan, TexasPoker, Invader & Skittles which may appeal to you. 
It is a visual basic coded-driven pinball game. It's all freeware for non-profit use only. 
You may also find them with AtGames if they are still being used by them. 

